{"tid":179199,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拒迪科爾探望 抗癌鬥士：唔想佢見我病樣","createTime":"2017-03-30T05:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T06:45:58.000Z","uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f607fccfb4c2d2d8c64b85903f661c37efd91300","tid":179199,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:41:57.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=a4824766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】「抗癌小勇士」也有軟弱時。5歲的癌症患者巴特利羅利為了不想偶像迪科爾的到自己的病容，拒絕了對方在周三探望自己。<br />\n<br />\n新特蘭擁躉巴特利（Bradley Lowery）的抗癌twitter於周三的新推文指：「巴特利的情況很差，差得要取消好朋友的探訪，因為巴特利不想對方看到自己的慘況。聽到他這樣說，真的心碎了。」<br />\n<br />\n文中的好朋友，正是「黑貓」射手迪科爾（Jermain Defoe）。<br />\n<br />\n3天前，巴特利才度過了人生最愉快的其中一天。在周日的世盃外，重新入選英格蘭的34歲老兵迪科爾排頭位帶同巴特利進場；而前者也沒有令好朋友失望，為「三獅兵團」先開紀錄，球隊終以2:0擊敗立陶宛。<br />\n<br />\n巴特利在2013年患上神經母細胞瘤，今年再被診斷出不幸多生了一個腫瘤在背部。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484ef2dd3046598d5e8c93c58afcf2197b77c2ca","tid":179199,"uid":53774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0950be5b9acbe4f0430e211032ea325d196ba4","tid":179199,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:57:35.000Z","msg":"5歲就咁堅強<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90fbdbb4f74e0b599e47f57a116640d9e71efe2","tid":179199,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:08:21.000Z","msg":"收到風阿丙早一步靜靜雞探左佢<br />\n所以人哋無興趣見過氣老嘢"},{"pid":"43c772d414cc7f5928185bc569d54284939914cb","tid":179199,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:08:27.000Z","msg":"點解咁多小朋友都身患絕症<br />\n係得呢個小朋友比人煲到咁大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal